<TEXT>
<P>
A man suspected in the bludgeon-and-slashing death of his former girlfriend and 
the brief disappearance of their daughter was found dead, his arm cut at an 
artery, authorities said Thursday. Richard R. Mowery, 24, of Colton was found 
dead Wednesday about 4:23 p.m. on the old railroad right-of-way in the 1000 
block of Valley Drive in Hermosa Beach, police spokesman Phil Lonzello said. 
</P>
<P>
