ex-girlfriend, Crystal Robinson, 27, at her mobile home in a park on Reche 
Canyon Road, police said. Witnesses said Mowery was seen that day taking his 
and Robinson's 1-year-old daughter Sarah from the mobile home, Colton police 
spokeswoman Misty King said. The baby was found alive Tuesday at a Redondo 
Beach motel, her skull fractured in five places, Hermosa Beach police said. 
