STATES -- IMMIGRATION; ILLEGAL ALIENS -- LOS ANGELES; ARRESTS -- LOS ANGELES; 
SMUGGLING; POLICE COMMUNITY RELATIONS; HOSTAGES -- LOS ANGELES 
</P>
