Reagan and Ford, before dedication of his presidential library in Yorba Linda. 
; Photo, Richard Nixon, with grandchildren Christopher Cox, left, and Alex 
Eisenhower, waves to crowd from window of boyhood home in Yorba Linda. KARI 
RENE HALL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Advocate for the homeless Ted Hayes is 
arrested outside Nixon dinner in Century City. J ALBERT DIAZ / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
