KIDNAPINGS -- MEXICO; CAMARENA, ENRIQUE; ALVAREZ MACHAIN, HUMBERTO; DRUG 
ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- MEXICO 
</P>
