<HEADLINE>
<P>
MIXED REVIEWS ON NIXON AND WATERGATE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Until I viewed the shining, clean-shaven image of Richard Nixon in your View 
section today, I had not gained full appreciation of the ancient Greek practice 
of political exile. 
</P>
<P>
Let's find a media-proof island for the guy who brought new meaning to White 
House corruption and has left a legacy of mistrust which has undermined the 
Presidency of the United States. 
</P>
<P>
PAUL R. GURIAN 
</P>
<P>
Hollywood 
</P>
