</P>
<P>
MEN'S SWIMMING 
</P>
<P>
Eric Diehl, Mission Viejo. 
</P>
<P>
WOMEN'S SWIMMING 
</P>
<P>
Janet Evans, Placentia. 
</P>
<P>
MEN'S TRACK AND FIELD 
</P>
<P>
Sheldon Blockburger, Newport Beach; Tonie Campbell, Irvine; Jim Doehring, San 
Clemente; Doug Nordquist, La Habra; Jay Thorson, Laguna Beach. 
</P>
<P>
WOMEN'S TRACK AND FIELD 
</P>
<P>
PattiSue Plumer, Newport Beach; Mary Slaney, Garden Grove; Karin Smith, Laguna 
Niguel. 
</P>
<P>
