Gillett Sells Baltimore TV Station: Gillett Group signed a letter of intent to 
sell NBC affiliate WMAR-TV in Baltimore for $154.7 million to Scripps Howard 
Broadcasting Co., a subsidiary of E. W. Scripps Co., the Cincinnati-based 
