<P>
ANITA BAKER FIGHTS STAGE FRIGHT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Singer Anita Baker says she battles paralyzing fear every time she goes on 
stage. 
</P>
<P>
"If I let fear stop me I would never leave my house," the Grammy winner said 
Thursday on ABC's "Good Morning America." 
</P>
<P>
